OL,3,CSainsbury's to cut 3,000 jobs and
OL,4,Cclose in-store cafes
OL,6,FJob losses at the head office will
OL,7,Fhappen over the next few months, ITV
OL,8,FNews' Cari Davies reports
OL,10,FSainsbury's will cut 3,000 jobs and
OL,11,Fclose all of its in-store cafes, the
OL,12,Fsupermarket announced on Thursday.
OL,14,FThe redundancies would include a 20%
OL,15,Freduction in senior management roles
OL,16,Fas the supermarket giant plans to
OL,17,Ffocus on fewer, bigger roles to
OL,18,Fsimplify its head office and
OL,19,Fmanagement teams.
