OL,3,CSainsbury's to cut 3,000 jobs and
OL,4,Cclose in-store cafes
OL,6,FSainsbury's also said it will close
OL,7,Fits 61 remaining cafes as most
OL,8,Fshoppers do not use them, it said.
OL,10,FJob losses at the head office will
OL,11,Fhappen over the next few months.
OL,13,FThe layoffs represent around 2% of the
OL,14,Fcompany's current workforce of 148,000
OL,15,Femployees.
OL,17,FThe retailer's patisserie, hot food
OL,18,Fand pizza counters in-store are also
OL,19,Fset to close, with the most popular
OL,20,Fitems to be available in the aisles
OL,21,Finstead.
