OL,3,CSainsbury's to cut 3,000 jobs and
OL,4,Cclose in-store cafes
OL,6,FThe cuts come after Sainsbury's
OL,7,Fannounced its "biggest ever" Christmas
OL,8,Ftrading period and said profit for the
OL,9,Ffull year would likely be between
OL,10,F#1.01 billion and #1.06 billion
OL,11,Fearlier in January.
OL,13,FBut the supermarket is also trying to
OL,14,Flower costs by #1 billion a year after
OL,15,Fcutting at least 1,500 roles in 2024,
OL,16,Fmostly from a contact centre in
OL,17,FCheshire.
