OL,11,FSainsbury's Chief Executive, Simon
OL,12,FRoberts, said the supermarket was
OL,13,Ffacing a "particularly challenging
OL,14,Fcost environment" as it moves forward
OL,15,Fwith its company strategy.
OL,17,F"We have had to make tough choices
OL,18,Fabout where we can afford to invest
OL,19,Fand where we need to do things
OL,20,Fdifferently to make our business more
OL,21,Fefficient and effective," he said.
